 />\n同埋現實係更加少所謂既大器晚成"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:23:47.000Z","msg":"我覺得環境唔同好難用以前d偉人黎做例子"},{"pid":"0d0180afe750f5d60d66dddd13608d8b21e416dd","tid":686344,"uid":89957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:25:16.000Z","msg":"叫佢玩dark soul，死一次温15分鐘書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3976f3de0bba7691f37ee3eb9bbdb6f052dffed5","tid":686344,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:25:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}